	1. wget XXXXXXXX.tar.gz  
	2. tar -zxvf XXXXXXXX.tar.gz
	3. configure --prefix=/home/XXXX
	, where you want to install. You can also include other options 
	4. make distclean 
	Remove all environments installed by configure
	5. make
	Compile; if it is failed, "make clean" and "make" again.
	6. make clean
	Cancellation of make
	7. make install
	Installation
	8. make uninstall
	Uninstallation 
	
	
	Reference : http://areumgury.blogspot.com/2012/10/blog-post.html
